<br>
CoL inefficient?  against 1 maybe (135 mana / 137 dmg), but think that you're doing 4 of these...  135 mana / 548 dmg - a 4dmg : 1 mana ratio.  That's around 4500 dmg / kite at lvl 29.  Try telling ANYONE else that you can do 4500 dmg without getting hit OR running out of mana, and they won't believe you. heh. <p><br>Aniar Orrenson
